<item>
            <title>[SYNAPSE-1109] WSA:From header is missing when sending a request to an endpoint </title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SYNAPSE-1109</link>
                <project id="12310201" key="SYNAPSE">Synapse</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;When a From value is set in the message context (e.g. with MessageContext.setFrom) before it is sent to an endpoint the value isn&apos;t used in the resulting request. This is due to the fact that the Axis2FlexibleMEPClient clones the message context before sending it and the&#160;MessageHelper.clonePartially doesn&apos;t copy the From value from the source message context to the cloned message context.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
